{"tid":1044574,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【機會嚟喇】麻省理工學生研發《哈利波特》分類帽 霍格華茲入學禮成真","createTime":"2019-03-03T04:12:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-03T05:55:52.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1342dd40b25853bf0566f59883d59f3b15977ca6","tid":1044574,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T04:12:39.000Z","msg":"《哈利波特》系列建構出奇幻魔法世界觀，多年來一直深受大人小朋友歡迎，霍格華茲亦成為不少人夢想入讀的最高學府，近日麻省理工一名學生成功研發分類帽，實現戲中分學院的橋段。<br />\n麻省理工博士研究生Nataliya Kosmyna早前設計出名為「Thinking Hat」的機械帽，透過非侵入式的電極裝置分析用戶的腦部活動，從而以機器學習（Machine Learning）模擬用戶的思維，原意是為了用作提升學生的自信心。<br />\n不過為了吸引更多人參與研究，工程師花29.99美金（約230港元）網購一頂《哈利波特》的分類帽，結合機械裝置，並參考J.K.羅琳（J.K. Rowling）<a href=\"http://主理的官網Pottermore.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%B8%BB%E7%90%86%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%98%E7%B6%B2Pottermore.com&d=96kHarChHvhp0Q8MKJCyEJnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=881d35f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">主理的官網Pottermore.com</a>的選擇題，設計出一系列可以區分用戶應屬哪個霍格華茲學院的題目，完成問題後，分類帽上以藍牙連接的擴音器更會宣佈學院，實現一眾魔法迷最期待的畫面。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190302/large/1551523969_3fff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190302%2Flarge%2F1551523969_3fff.jpg&h=a2c44b2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190302/large/1551523974_0481.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190302%2Flarge%2F1551523974_0481.jpg&h=b9979a6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190302/large/1551523969_8a35.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190302%2Flarge%2F1551523969_8a35.jpg&h=8055270a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190302/large/1551523974_8627.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190302%2Flarge%2F1551523974_8627.jpg&h=54e0280d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f7bad22053a9ec2a36e3a5ec8c199cc4ad348f1f","tid":1044574,"uid":82068,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T05:22:17.000Z","msg":"幾型<br />\n啱班毒撚30歲自動轉職做魔法師用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92b0ba44f7875d86834ec2702e1dddb001e5007c","tid":1044574,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T05:53:20.000Z","msg":"真係有效嘅話會分晒同一類人入同一學院都幾搞笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40ecc9fdd9ec9101eef33ddad1b111e48aefef01","tid":1044574,"uid":52358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T05:55:52.000Z","msg":"溝支那妹自動歸類史箂哲林<br />\n利申 大賢者<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}